Pre-trained Model Decision Tree. Flow: Start -> Need Full Control/Privacy? Yes -> Self-hosted (Llama, Mistral). No -> Need Lowest Latency? Yes -> Edge (Phi-3, Gemma). No -> Scale >1M Req/Day? Yes -> Hybrid (Cloud + Self-hosted). No -> Start with Cloud API (OpenAI, Anthropic) -> Monitor Costs -> Migrate when needed. Decision diamonds, action boxes. German labels, realistic thresholds.